The **2008 Digital Spy Soap Awards** recognized outstanding achievements in the world of soap operas. The winners included:

- **'Best Soap'**: [EastEnders](/EastEnders)
- **'Most Popular Actor'**: [James Sutton](/James_Sutton_(actor)) ([John Paul McQueen](/John_Paul_McQueen) in [Hollyoaks](/Hollyoaks))
