- **'Sexiest Male'**: [Scott Maslen](/Scott_Maslen) ([Jack Branning](/Jack_Branning) in [EastEnders](/EastEnders))
- **'Sexiest Female'**: [Roxanne McKee](/Roxanne_McKee) ([Louise Summers](/Louise_Summers) in [Hollyoaks](/Hollyoaks))
- **'Best Newcomer'**: [Rita Simons](/Rita_Simons) ([Roxy Mitchell](/Roxy_Mitchell) in [EastEnders](/EastEnders))
